      "Inventory reached 1.55M units, a 4.5-month supply; the Housing Affordability Index rose to 105.6 from 97.5 a year earlier",
      "The 30-year fixed averaged 6.44% in May 2026, up from 6.33% in April but below 6.82% a year ago",
      "All-equity REITs returned only ~2.3% in 2025, with data centers down 14.1%; health care led at 28.5% and industrial at 17%",
